    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LayoutParams" kindref="compound">LayoutParams</ref> is the base handle class for all layout parameter types. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It provides a common base for <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AbsoluteLayoutParams" kindref="compound">AbsoluteLayoutParams</ref>, <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1FlexLayoutParams" kindref="compound">FlexLayoutParams</ref>, <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1GridLayoutParams" kindref="compound">GridLayoutParams</ref>, and <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1StackLayoutParams" kindref="compound">StackLayoutParams</ref>. Use with <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1a772712edaeac7bad4b3c19632394d336" kindref="member">View::SetLayoutParams()</ref> and <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1a3aca1f83952f8c5a90bc6641ad8fda91" kindref="member">View::GetLayoutParams()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
